## Quick Reference

### Core Principles
- Everything must be typesafe
- Follow SOLID principles  
- Only use Yarn for package management
- Persian RTL-only layout (html lang=fa-IR)
- Use Tailwind for all styling
- Implement accessibility features
- No todo's or placeholders in final code

### Key Technologies
- ReactJS & NextJS
- TypeScript (no 'any' types)
- TailwindCSS
- Persian localization
- RTL layout support